Items.c: <[>這裡地盤不穩,後方又是山谷,要是真打起來可就危險了。得隱開他的注意力,再另外找機會逃走。<]>
Items.mt: <[>The ground here is unstable, and the valley is behind us, so it would be dangerous if we really fight. We have to hide his attention and find another chance to escape. <]>
